{"tid":297500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經]如果俾你選多次，你想返去細個定大個？","createTime":"2017-06-25T13:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T14:02:24.000Z","uid":108312,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aba3714ee3e2c404c9065ecdad5e70c6d395cafd","tid":297500,"uid":108312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"假設你得返十年命，哩十年你唔會再長大<br />\n但可以俾你選要做小學雞嘅自己<br />\n定係要長大出黎做嘢嘅自己？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評:小學雞嘅自己，日日無憂無慮，唔駛擔心錢嘅問題，返學，食飯，玩，訓<br />\n星期六、日放假<br />\n但就乜都要俾老豆，老母，老師管住<br />\n夜少少返屋企又唔得<br />\n放假想打吓機又要擔心功課未做晒<br />\n又要應付默書，測驗，考試<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負皮:出黎做嘢嘅自己，人大咗屋企冇管咁嚴，唔返屋企講聲就ok，放假無後顧之憂，打機就打機，訓就訓，自己搵錢自己洗，買新機冇人阻你<br />\n日日返工對住啲閪人閪老細，做啲你根本唔願做嘅事，又擔心搵錢唔夠人多，樓價離你愈來愈遠，老豆老母又開始老，冇以前咁好活力"},{"pid":"ad55a60263865726006f94330f16f7cd91cde139","tid":297500,"uid":3268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:51:58.000Z","msg":"大十年<br />\n近退休一大步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好退休5年內死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n減少浪費地球資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7507795d7c46f8e677788774ef044f59f6cf38","tid":297500,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"小學雞又太細，16歲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7991767417af03b18b1b53004be12bcf330ee037","tid":297500,"uid":108312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"自己先黎個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己小學雞時期唔係特別快樂，讀書壓力都大<br />\n唔係鐘意讀書<br />\n出咗黎做嘢起碼自由啲，自己搵錢可以買自己鐘意嘅嘢，細個問呀媽攞錢會覺得好對佢唔住<br />\n不過呀爸呀媽可唔可以唔好再老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8cdc6601a7f53751b743daffd746e3e27bc325","tid":297500,"uid":108312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學雞又太細，16歲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁先可以做到對比嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n16歲其實都好大個，乖嘅要擔心讀書成績，升大學問題，曳嘅都變mk街童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f404165380c8f6a33651a9ced5157819295f99","tid":297500,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"緊係返中小學個十年, 我夠膽講所有人最開心嘅回憶都係呢段時間發生"},{"pid":"66cae22252de910c916ccc63e33969755634aadf","tid":297500,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"中學"}]}